name: BEATLIFE #2 // R U I D O S
description:
Second edition from the BEATLIFE trilogy, a compilation of beats produced by zilladxg. For lovers of Hip Hop, Beats, Lo-Fi Textures and Experimental Sounds.
BEATLIFE #2 is the most complex and intriguing edition. 
zilladxg demonstrates all his sampling skills and takes us to a dense and psychedelic landscape around 10 beats.

Digital Collage: @gessalustavo (1857x1857 - JPEG)
Beats: @zilladxg
Year: 2017
